title: Circling the Bush: A RHONJ Shore Recap!

description:
Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of New Jersey, which features the cast at the Jersey Shore, a producer stepping in, and Frankie Jr.'s ball gag. RHOC is off this week, but we have plenty of Jersey to discuss!
